+/*
+ *  HID driver for "PHILIPS MCE USB IR Receiver- Spinel plus" remotes
+ *
+ *  Copyright (c) 2010 Panagiotis Skintzos
+ *
+ *  Renamed to Spinel, cleanup and modified to also support
+ *  Spinel Plus 0471:20CC by Stephan Raue 2012.
+ */
+
